WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.869
Hey, good morning everybody again. I'm

00:00:02.869 --> 00:00:02.879
going to

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:05.150
do another video here; I'm

00:00:05.160 --> 00:00:07.190
doing them back to back. This is

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.570
something the Lord brought to my

00:00:08.580 --> 00:00:11.150
attention yesterday in my prayer time. He

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:13.910
told me that in the summer

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:16.369
of

00:00:16.369 --> 00:00:16.379
2022—I

00:00:16.379 --> 00:00:19.609
believe it was about this time

00:00:19.619 --> 00:00:21.290
last year, well, a little bit

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:22.670
before because it was probably

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:25.910
around April or so—he came to me

00:00:25.920 --> 00:00:27.710
when I was praying and said, 'Brandon,

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:30.349
there's going to be a massive increase in the

00:00:30.359 --> 00:00:32.930
near future coming up. Oil is going to go

00:00:32.940 --> 00:00:35.389
to $200 a

00:00:35.389 --> 00:00:35.399
barrel.'He

00:00:35.399 --> 00:00:38.030
said the Prince of Saudi

00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:40.970
Arabia is going to go against the United

00:00:40.980 --> 00:00:44.030
States, and

00:00:44.040 --> 00:00:46.250
they're going to cause an oil shortage.

00:00:46.260 --> 00:00:48.650
They're going to go with

00:00:48.660 --> 00:00:50.510
Russia

00:00:50.510 --> 00:00:50.520
and

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:53.150
China in this, and it's

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:54.709
like a secret mission against the United

00:00:54.719 --> 00:00:58.209
States. But I saw

00:00:58.219 --> 00:01:01.549
the price of gas go to almost seven

00:01:01.559 --> 00:01:04.729
dollars a gallon again. I saw things like

00:01:04.729 --> 00:01:04.739
the

00:01:04.739 --> 00:01:07.850
price of commodities

00:01:07.850 --> 00:01:07.860
rising

00:01:07.860 --> 00:01:08.870
because they're trying to control

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:10.969
inflation.

00:01:10.979 --> 00:01:13.010
This is all part of the

00:01:13.020 --> 00:01:15.469
global economic

00:01:15.479 --> 00:01:18.469
reset;

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:20.510
it's part of the digital platform

00:01:20.520 --> 00:01:22.609
they're

00:01:22.609 --> 00:01:22.619
doing—creating

00:01:22.619 --> 00:01:24.710
new digital currencies

00:01:24.710 --> 00:01:24.720
and

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:27.170
weakening the dollar.

00:01:27.180 --> 00:01:29.630
I don't know how all

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.550
this happens; I'm just saying these

00:01:31.550 --> 00:01:31.560
are

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:34.130
the parts that I see. The Lord

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:36.289
told me that, like I said, oil would go

00:01:36.289 --> 00:01:36.299
to

00:01:36.299 --> 00:01:38.990
$200 a barrel and gas was going to go very,

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.510
very high, so

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:44.090
I just wanted to warn you about some

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:47.149
of this stuff. Number two: this was three

00:01:47.159 --> 00:01:49.609
or four weeks ago, I believe. I was

00:01:49.619 --> 00:01:52.670
praying and the Lord showed me, 'I

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:55.850
need you to pray for

00:01:55.850 --> 00:01:55.860
Italy.'I

00:01:55.860 --> 00:01:58.609
said, 'What's going on with

00:01:58.619 --> 00:02:00.590
Italy, Lord?'and he showed

00:02:00.590 --> 00:02:00.600
me—I

00:02:00.600 --> 00:02:02.270
had an open-eye vision

00:02:02.270 --> 00:02:02.280
again—that

00:02:02.280 --> 00:02:04.730
there's a massive

00:02:04.740 --> 00:02:07.550
volcano that's about to happen. I saw

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:10.249
a coastline on the water,

00:02:10.259 --> 00:02:13.790
and there's a massive volcano there.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:16.430
He told me this is going to

00:02:16.440 --> 00:02:19.010
happen, and he said there will be signs

00:02:19.020 --> 00:02:21.110
right before there's a massive explosion.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:24.410
I saw it explode huge,

00:02:24.420 --> 00:02:27.830
and he kept having me pray over the

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:30.530
ocean. There's something about

00:02:30.540 --> 00:02:34.010
the water around Italy that is

00:02:34.020 --> 00:02:35.449
very dangerous; there's

00:02:35.459 --> 00:02:38.150
like a volcano in that water, and this is

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:39.890
going to shoot off and

00:02:39.900 --> 00:02:43.610
cause major devastation. It's

00:02:43.620 --> 00:02:46.610
going to be very serious. I've

00:02:46.620 --> 00:02:48.949
been praying for the people of Italy to

00:02:48.959 --> 00:02:51.170
wake up. If they are Christian—or if they're

00:02:51.170 --> 00:02:51.180
not—pray

00:02:51.180 --> 00:02:53.089
that they are where they're supposed

00:02:53.099 --> 00:02:55.430
to be so that they will leave when this

00:02:55.440 --> 00:02:58.490
thing goes off. There's a huge town

00:02:58.500 --> 00:03:00.250
or city

00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:04.130
on the edge of the water where I saw

00:03:04.140 --> 00:03:07.729
this volcano go off. There will be

00:03:07.739 --> 00:03:11.750
signs, maybe even on the news in Italy,

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:15.350
about some rumblings around that

00:03:15.350 --> 00:03:15.360
area—some

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:18.050
earthquakes

00:03:18.060 --> 00:03:20.990
or tremors—to pre-warn that something

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:24.530
big is going to happen. Do not ignore

00:03:24.540 --> 00:03:27.290
this. It is very

00:03:27.300 --> 00:03:30.890
serious; what I saw is very serious.

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:33.770
If you have little tremors, if you

00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:35.630
start having a lot of tremors, and you

00:03:35.640 --> 00:03:38.149
start seeing smoke or there's something

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:40.009
going on,

00:03:40.739 --> 00:03:45.110
take heed. Be

00:03:45.110 --> 00:03:45.120
forewarned;

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:47.330
I'm trying to tell you this is

00:03:47.340 --> 00:03:49.550
going to be a major event, an

00:03:49.550 --> 00:03:49.560
end-time

00:03:49.560 --> 00:03:52.070
event. I don't know when it's going to

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:55.369
happen; I wish I did. I'm sorry; I only

00:03:55.379 --> 00:03:59.869
see in part and I hear in part, and so

00:03:59.869 --> 00:03:59.879
it's

00:03:59.879 --> 00:04:01.729
just stuff I'm praying over. That's

00:04:01.739 --> 00:04:03.350
basically what I had; those are two

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:06.110
little things. I have another

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:08.449
video I'm about to do; it'll be my third

00:04:08.459 --> 00:04:11.330
video, but this is the positive

00:04:11.340 --> 00:04:15.439
one. Have a blessed day. Bye-bye.

